Package: TimeTeller
Title: Inferring circadian clock phase and dysfunction from single samples
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vadim", "Vasilyev", email = "vadim.vasilyev@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Vadim Vasilyev <vadim.vasilyev@warwick.ac.uk>
Description: Machine learning tool that analyses the local circadian clock as a system. 
    It aims to estimate the circadian clock phase and the level of dysfunction from a single sample by modelling the multi-dimensional state of the clock.
